{"id":"1b161598-0127-4dbe-9008-d3a88b110c9b","name":"Lysander ✧ The Rising Tide","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/7l3PVTXSuIiyRk0VlgKCv.webp\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><em>\"When the severed light remembers its name, and the hollow crown bends in grief, the gate that was closed shall breathe once more. </em></strong><br><strong><em>From divided blood, a single truth shall rise, and all that was bound apart will be unmade.\"</em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/MOYO2PiMguvNpotOoLQSt.webp\"></p><p class=\"div _characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><u>SYNOPSIS</u></strong></p><p class=\"div _characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Lysander wasn't there when the first prophecy came to his mother, but the legend has been passed on for all of the Dark Realm to know.<br><br>And now he stands in the presence of another history unfolding, this time with a second prophecy. Yet there seems to be more than meets the eye as he gets news that a revolution is conspiring behind the scenes.<br><br>Those who never accepted the union of his parents, both demon and angel, have teamed up.<br><br>With Evangeline and your brother at the forefront of it all, he starts to question where you stand in all of this.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/MOYO2PiMguvNpotOoLQSt.webp\"></p><p class=\"div _input_1uufu_102\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><u>INTROS:</u></strong><br><br>1. Written for She/He pronouns.<br>2. Written for They/Them pronouns.</p><p class=\"div _characterInfoShinyBox_9gldz_86\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>「 THE LORE (IN TIME ORDER) 」</strong></p><p class=\"div _input_1uufu_102\" style=\"text-align: center;\">SEASON ONE:<br><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/6f19b29c-3e5b-45fa-a216-f9eda3555434_character-kali-%E2%9C%A7-the-beginning\" target=\"_blank\">The Beginning</a> | <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/a87ef9c3-9430-4648-8a47-ba308560e2aa_character-kali\" target=\"_blank\">The War</a> | <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/65f345e2-8245-45d2-972c-92224a2bbb55_character-kali-%E2%9C%A7-the-depressed-angel\" target=\"_blank\">The Depressed Angel</a> | <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/089a6018-a778-4974-bfa9-2ccea880f39b_character-kali-%E2%9C%A7-the-proposal\" target=\"_blank\">The Proposal</a><br><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/81153feb-b7b4-4dbd-a6ab-3dad2f0e82e6_character-kali-%E2%9C%A7-the-wedding\" target=\"_blank\">The Wedding</a> | <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/1b6fc6e8-f3f7-48ac-b391-becc85ec97ac_character-kali\" target=\"_blank\">The Jealous Lord</a> | <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/597a55f3-a161-4df0-aec1-2c84c0fa867d_character-kali\" target=\"_blank\">The Pregnant Angel </a>| <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/a6fbfbbc-619f-457a-a216-370869cf38ea_character-lysander\" target=\"_blank\">The Crown Prince</a></p><p class=\"div _input_1uufu_102\" style=\"text-align: center;\">SEASON TWO:<br><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/c32e6f4c-9525-43d8-92b2-a6c7563092fe_character-kali-%E2%9C%A7-the-resurgence\" target=\"_blank\">The Resurgence</a> | The Rising Tide | <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/16ef0a74-e1be-4e83-a66e-486cf8473934_character-kali-%E2%9C%A7-the-second-war\" target=\"_blank\">The Second War</a> <span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);\">| </span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/896a15ec-58b6-4e2c-b074-e1